List.Description:
Gift certificates make the perfect last minute gift! Gift certificates give them exactly what they want and emailing them guarantees that they'll get it on time.

Gift certificates are good on any product sold on Wine.com. When you provide an email address with the shipping information at checkout, a message will be sent that evening to the recipient with the gift certificate number, dollar amount and a personal message from you.

But you don't need their email address to give a gift certificate. All certificates are sent out with a gift card and your personal gift message via First Class mail. Please allow three to five days for delivery.

Note: Gift certificates are not redeemable for cash. Only one gift certificate may be redeemed per order. When placing an order using a gift certificate, please note that a credit card is required even if the gift certificate covers the full amount of the order. As long as the value of the gift certificate exceeds the price of the product purchased, no charges will be made to the credit card. Unused balances of gift certificates will appear as a credit in your Wine.com account.

For larger denominations, please contact our customer service department directly at 1-800-592-5870.
